**\n- Use dynamic prompt syntax/wildcards for advanced prompting\n- Or write standard prompts directly—dynamic features are optional\n\n**Alternative Setup:**\nIf you don't need dynamic prompts or prefer not to install custom nodes, replace the node DynamicPrompts Text Box (Positive Prompt) with the standard **CLIP Text Encode** node and connect it to the positive conditioning input on the **WAN ImageToVideo** node."],"color":"#322","bgcolor":"#533"},{"id":161,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[1649.338623046875,-501.681884765625],"size":[465.369384765625,261.1520080566406],"flags":{},"order":4,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["## Batch Image Loader\n\nAutomatically loads images sequentially from a folder with each execution.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n- Set **Int value** to `0`\n- Set **control** to `increment`\n- Specify **source folder** path (containing your images)\n- Configure **Dimensions** as needed\n\n**Usage:**\nIf your folder contains 16 images, simply run the workflow 16 times. The counter increments automatically with each run, loading the next image in sequence. No manual loading required.\n\n**If not needed:**\nDisable via Fast Groups Bypasser and enable the usual **Load Image** node."],"color":"#322","bgcolor":"#533"},{"id":163,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[-168.15200805664062,-399.80792236328125],"size":[260.3477783203125,159.51837158203125],"flags":{},"order":5,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["## SmoothMix Wan 2.2 \n\n**does not need speed LoRAs**. \n\nDisable the node when using SmoothMix."],"color":"#322","bgcolor":"#533"},{"id":155,"type":"Any Switch (rgthree)","pos":[1780.841064453125,374.540283203125],"size":[250.04998779296875,106],"flags":{"collapsed":true},"order":22,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"dir":3,"name":"any_01","type":"IMAGE","link":298},{"dir":3,"name":"a